                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-695-18510303 t18510303-695-punishment-39"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAM RANDALL</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18510303-695-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
